1. Python 3 Porting Database
  2. python2-typing

Package python2-typing

This package will not be ported to Python 3. We can do without it – see if there is an alternative listed in the notes.

If you think it would be good to port it anyway, get in touch with the upstream!


See python2-typing in the Fedora Pagure, or go directly to the corresponding spec file.

Note

The typing module is part of the standard library in Python 3.5+; no need for this backport there.
